*GOAL*

*As a…*survey user

*I want…*the thank you message on the results page to address me by my first name

*So that…*I feel acknowledged and appreciated for my participation in the survey
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#eae6ff}
*SCOPE*

*In scope:*

# Retrieval of the participant's first name input from the landing page.
# Integration of the participant's first name into the thank you message displayed on the results page.
# Development of logic to dynamically insert the participant's first name into the thank you message.
# Testing to ensure accurate rendering of personalised thank you messages based on participant input.

[Content here.|https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vj8XKR5acyQgYPT7U3OzXCoCs6jNZGzw53JcIvNgZu8/edit]

*Out of scope:*

* Personalisation of the thank you message beyond the participant's first name.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#deebff}
*ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA*

*Given* I input my first name on the landing page, *When* I complete the survey, *Then* I should observe my first name dynamically inserted into the thank you message on the results page.

*Given* I input a different first name on the landing page, *When* I finish the survey, *Then* I should see the updated first name reflected in the thank you message on the results page.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#fffae6}
*TECH CONSIDERATIONS*
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#e3fcef}
*GOAL*

*As a…*survey user

*I want…*the survey questions to be personalised with the name of my company

*So that…*I feel more engaged and connected to the survey content.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#eae6ff}
*SCOPE*

*In scope:*

# Identification of survey questions containing generic company references (e.g., "the company," "your company," “the organisation” etc.).
# Development of logic to dynamically replace generic company references with the user's company name.
# Integration of participant-provided company name from the landing page input field into survey question text.
# Testing to ensure accurate replacement of company names and proper rendering of personalised survey questions.



*Out of scope:*

* Customization of survey questions beyond the scope of company name replacement
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#deebff}
*ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA*

+*Scenario 1*+

*Given* I input my company name on the landing page, *When* I proceed to the survey questions, *Then* I should observe my company name dynamically inserted into relevant survey question text.

*Given* I enter a different company name on the landing page, *When* I navigate to the survey questions, *Then* I should see the updated company name reflected in the survey question text.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#fffae6}
*TECH CONSIDERATIONS*
